			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>I&#8217;ve already solved my problem by myself.</p>
<p>The solution was HasLayout! So adding &#8220;height:1%&#8221; to &#8220;#navbar li:hover li a, #navbar li.hover li a{&#8221; solved the problem.</p>
<p>Now the menu works fine in every browser!</p>
							</section><!-- .comment-content -->

			
